C & J is a Jamaican restaurant on Utica Ave in the East Flatbush section of Brooklyn, NY between Linden Boulevard and Church Avenue. It specializes in authentic Jamaican cuisine and seats are available for dining. Takeout is also available. It is a stone's throw from Bobby's Department Store and T-Mobile on the same block. Accessible by the B46 bus and the B35 bus on Church Avenue.
